title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your desire to break from stodgy routines and conventional answers is likely irrepressible today. Your restlessness might direct you to investigate distant places and unusual beliefs. You could even make a bizarre statement just for the sake of shocking your colleagues and friends. However, be careful that your craving for the edge doesnt lead to rash behavior. Let your emotions roam free internally but filter your actions to ensure youre heading toward what you want, not merely away from what youre tired of experiencing. Athlete Bo Jackson said, Set your goals high, and dont stop until you get there. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
